author: @saraheal1981
text:
SMTreatRenjunBetter *I expect SM to focus more on Renjun and care about Renjun's feelings more than this* cause of the amount of activities, content, promotion of Renjun, the unique opportunity to start doing new things in entertainment industry and participation in nct albums. If you compare it, *RENJUN STILL GETS IT MUCH LESS THAN THE OTHER MEMBERS IN NCT.* And many times it shows that you don't care about Renjun's feelings at all and giving priority to him as the last priority such as 
â€” *He debuted 6 years but only 9 videos* the company 'intended to make for Renjun' and he's the owner of that content
â€” *Renjun is the only member in nct dream that has never had content he owns and has 'multiple ep'* or is a moderator of that content (like chenji, JSMR, As chenle wishes, justdoit, 37.5MHz, sun&moon and show!euMarkJungsim) even though he has many activities in his daily life and has always been praised for his variety sense
â€” The nct show *Renjun only participated in 7 of 29 content and was the only vocal line who had never participated in music space* (1 of 6 mb who didn't participate)â€‹
â€” He debuted 6 years but there was *only 2 variety shows* in which he was 'representatives' of nct or dream unit and was chosen to participate (20190416 JTBC Idol Room and 2022 The Return of Superman all 3 eps for 41 mins) 
â€” *He only gets 1 sec vcr* in kcon@LA while the members are mc and has a special vcr longer than 3 mins
â€” *No ost., no NCT LAB, no feat. or collab with other artists, no series or drama, no mc. Renjun's solo activities that appears on smtown website has only one is to be a RenD at akdong seoul* 
â€” *Renjun is the only dream member who didn't get any special stage or special performance at sbs gayo* (MK-All i want Christmas, Universe/ JN-Universe, ë§›breakdance/ HC-ì°½ë°–ì„ë³´ë¼, Universe/ JM-Universe, ë§›breakdance/ CL-ì°½ë°–ì„ë³´ë¼/ JS-ë§›breakdance)â€‹ WHY???
â€” in the smtown concert *He only performed nct dream's songs without any special performances* although he can perform 12ì›”ì˜ ì¸ì‚¬ song
â€” in resonance *He isn't the center and has NO SCREENâ€‹ TIMEâ€‹*
â€”There is *NO BEHIND THE SCENES of Renjun's photoshoot with ELLE idol Digital magazine and doesn't receive any promotion from sm* even if it sells more than 200.000
â€” *He was excluded from CF filming* (cosmetic brand) 
â€” in the title song *Renjun has less and less vocal parts and has the least screen time* (both in MV and performance) despite his position being main vocalist and lead dancer
â€” *Ending fairy that Renjun only gets 1-2 times per comeback* and fans must always come out and ask for justice. Renjun to get the 2nd ending fairy while other members more than 4 timesâ€‹
â€” *Renjun has very few fancams from music shows,* even though his views are ranked 1-4 among all the members. When promoting comeback comes into 2nd week Renjun usually doesn't have a special fancam like facecam, ì–¼ë¹¡ì§ìº  and ì…ë•ì§ìº  while the other members have both a main fancam and a special fancam 
Other members may only have 1 or 2 problems like this, but Renjun has to face them all. I think this isn't what he deserves as an artist who debuted for 6 years. *Renjun should grow out of his solo activities like the other NCT members have.*
Renjun's fans are always ready to fully support Renjun's work. I think Renjun's fans have devoted quite a lot of money to support him. *SM entertainment should support Renjun fully*
